<span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-17006c3d-a551-40aa-95ca-93b79d69627f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-9c45080d-2daa-47e6-94db-dfeb671e2320\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-08f835d9-ac94-4f4f-b254-326c3c182a19\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eca655bf-4b91-44aa-a47a-4794d031c81f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e6b519b4-46a0-42fb-ae62-fe9eb3ac931e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>BB골</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bb888999-75ae-407c-8212-9bdcc20a0033\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-71553603-df94-469d-bbd0-5858723ec770\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">두께는 A골과 비슷한 5~5.5mm지만 B골 2중겹으로 구성되어 완충력과 강도가 더 뛰어납니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f0ccf8b1-b019-4134-8c86-567a6dbd51b6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.ne